Les portes de l'infirmerie.

34
00:04:23,379 --> 00:04:24,631
Salut, Dani.

35
00:04:25,089 --> 00:04:26,507
Je suis la Dre Reyes.

36
00:04:26,841 --> 00:04:29,135
Si tu t'assieds, je te détacherai la main.

37
00:04:43,024 --> 00:04:47,320
